If you’re having a hard time growing your glutes then start training them 2-3 times a week. Aside from barbell squats and deadlifts use these isolation exercises to grow!⁣
⁣
1️⃣ Single  leg dumbbell hip thrust 4x12 ⁣
⁣
2️⃣ RDL. The band helps keeping the glutes engaged on the way up. ⁣4x12
⁣
3️⃣ Wide squat. Light weight to keep glutes engaged to the max. 4x 8-12
⁣
4️⃣ Bulgarian split squat. 3x12 each leg 
⁣
5️⃣ Hip abductor. Leaning backwards targets the upper part of your glutes and leaning forward targets the middle. 4x15
The pain you feel today will be the strength you feel tomorrow👊🏾
